title: Photo Alert: Varun Dhawan & Natasha Dalal Celebrated Zoa Morani’s Birthday
text:
Shreemi Verma Mar . 30 . 2017 
Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal have been dating for years, and while the actor prefers to keep mum about his personal life, the two don’t shy away from making public appearances together. Recently, the couple celebrated actress Zoa Morani ‘s birthday with their group of friends and looked rather cute together. A post shared by Priyaankk Sharma (@priyaankksharma) on Mar 29, 2017 at 12:14am PDT 
Here they are!
